2.4 cubic ft.; finding aid; collection contains materials relating to Arnold's unsuccessful 1972 campaign for U.S. Congress.
University of Central Arkansas
Conway, Ark.
Gale Stewart papers, 1968-1986; .25 cubic ft.; finding aid; correspondence.
 



